Package: NFcriptomicsR
Title: A Comprehensive Shiny App for RNA-Seq Analysis of Neurofibroma Data
Version: 0.7.4
Authors@R: person("Alpay", "Temiz", email = "temizna@umn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    NFcriptomicsR provides an interactive Shiny interface for complete RNA-Seq analysis of 
     Neurofibroma data, including
     normalization, quality control, differential expression,
    gene expression visualization, pathway analysis, and GSEA using CRAN and Bioconductor tools.
